OL,4,Chouse on CCTV jailed for life for
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FTwo men who launched a "horrific"
OL,8,Farson attack on a family home in
OL,9,FWolverhampton, killing a 26-year-old
OL,10,Fman and leaving his mother with life-
OL,11,Fchanging injuries, have been jailed
OL,12,Ffor life.
OL,14,FDaniel Tatters was caught on a
OL,15,Fsecurity camera smashing and removing
OL,16,Fa bay window at the home of Akashdeep
OL,17,FSingh, before using a flammable liquid
OL,18,Fto engulf the living room in flames.
OL,20,FTatters was sentenced to life with a
OL,21,Fminimum term of 34 years.
