OL,7,FDale Francis, who acted as a driver
OL,8,Fand look-out at the scene, was
OL,9,Fsentenced to life with a minimum term
OL,10,Fof 36 years.
OL,12,FBoth men, who are from Stoke-on-Trent,
OL,13,Fwere both unanimously convicted of
OL,14,Fmurder, arson with intent to endanger
OL,15,Flife and attempted murder on Tuesday,
OL,16,Fafter jurors deliberated for more than
OL,17,Fnine hours.
