OL,4,Chouse on CCTV jailed for life for
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe judge told them: "The family are
OL,8,Fnow all traumatised by the death of
OL,9,FAkashdeep Singh.
OL,11,F"I am sure you intended to kill anyone
OL,12,Fwho found themselves in the house at
OL,13,Fthe time of the fire."
OL,15,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,16,Fthe court before the sentence,
OL,17,FAkashdeep's family said the fire at
OL,18,Fhis home was an act of "pure evil"
OL,19,Fmeant for someone else, which had left
OL,20,Fa normal family suffering
OL,21,F"unimaginable" pain and suffering.
