OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FA three-week trial at Wolverhampton
OL,8,FCrown Court was told that a security
OL,9,Fcamera filmed Daniel Tatters as he
OL,10,Fsmashed and removed a bay window at
OL,11,Fthe home of Akashdeep Singh, before
OL,12,Fusing a flammable liquid to engulf the
OL,13,Fliving room in flames.
OL,15,FMr Singh died in hospital hours later
OL,16,Fafter being trapped upstairs by the
OL,17,Fblaze at his home in Plascom Road in
OL,18,FEast Park in Wolverhampton, which the
OL,19,Fcourt heard may have been targeted by
OL,20,Fmistake.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
