OL,3,CPair caught setting fire to 'wrong'
OL,4,Chouse on CCTV jailed for life for
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FProsecutors alleged that Tatters, 26,
OL,8,Fand 37-year-old Francis had started
OL,9,Fthe fire at about 1am on June 25 last
OL,10,Fyear "as the outcome of a considered
OL,11,Fagreement" following several previous
OL,12,Fjourneys to familiarise themselves
OL,13,Fwith the area.
OL,15,FA lighter found by fire crews near the
OL,16,Fbay window was found to have Tatters's
OL,17,FDNA on it, while phone records, an in-
OL,18,Fcar tracking device and other CCTV
OL,19,Ffootage linked Francis, of Clare
OL,20,FStreet, Basford, Stoke-on-Trent, to
OL,21,Fthe attack.
