OL,4,Chouse on CCTV jailed for life for
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FTatters told jurors he had never been
OL,8,Fto Wolverhampton and had cut his hand
OL,9,Fon a glass pane while falling over in
OL,10,Fhis garden.
OL,12,FFrancis, whose barrister described the
OL,13,Fconsequences of the fire as tragic and
OL,14,Fhorrific, declined to give evidence,
OL,15,Fclaiming in a written statement he
OL,16,Fthought his accomplice only intended
OL,17,Fto "torch" a car.
