OL,7,FProsecutor Mark Heywood KC opened the
OL,8,Fcase at the start of the trial, saying
OL,9,Fthe defendants had travelled around 40
OL,10,Fmiles from Stoke-on-Trent in Francis's
OL,11,FVolkswagen Golf.
OL,13,FTatters visited the Royal Stoke
OL,14,FUniversity Hospital around two-and-a-
OL,15,Fhalf hours after the fire for
OL,16,Ftreatment for cuts to his fingers.
