OL,4,Chouse on CCTV jailed for life for
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FCCTV proved Tatters, who was staying
OL,8,Fat an address in Sneyd Green, Stoke-on-
OL,9,FTrent, went on foot to Plascom Road
OL,10,Fafter the Golf was parked in
OL,11,FSutherland Avenue, around a third of a
OL,12,Fmile away.
OL,14,FThe footage also showed the driver's
OL,15,Fdoor of the Golf being opened minutes
OL,16,Fbefore two figures were seen entering
OL,17,FEast Park at a location said to be a
OL,18,Fsix-minute walk to Plascom Road.
OL,20,F"Each of them shared the intention to
OL,21,Fmurder all the occupants"
